<item>
            <title>[LU-6667] ll_getname allocates too big of a buffer</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6667</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;__getname used in ll_getname allocated PATH_MAX sized 4k buffer that is overkill.&lt;br/&gt;
In fact we only need a single component of the pathname that could not be longer than 255 bytes, so only allocating 256 bytes should be enough.&lt;br/&gt;
Additionally need to check for strncpy_from_user negative return values while at that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
